      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and offers reliable transportation for someone looking for a solid value. While the engine and transmission are functional and the car drives well, the exterior shows some noticeable wear, including minor scratches and faded paint. The interior also shows signs of use, such as some staining on the upholstery and wear on the dashboard. It has been maintained regularly, but it is not in showroom condition, making it a practical choice for a daily commuter or a first car.",
