    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies. This example is paired with a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Mechanically, the car is robust: the critical VANOS system has been serviced, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced to ensure chassis rigidity. It sits on a refreshed suspension with upgraded bushings, maintaining the precise turn-in and neutral handling balance characteristic of the E46 platform. While the exterior shows minor stone chips and light wear consistent with spirited use, the powertrain and drivetrain remain in excellent health, having undergone regular valve adjustments and fluid analysis.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
